node.text: As an entrepreneur, do you struggle going on vacations..? If so, this message is for you! I made this video a few years ago, but thought it was appropriate to post, now that we’re half way through the summer… in hopes to remind you that you’re not weird… you’re an Entrepreneur, and that’s ok!!

node.text:
The last 12 months have been hard for many…

But for those who were at FHL, we were prepared… One month before the lockdown, we had 5,000 ‘Funnel Hackers’ together at FHL, and @TonyRobbins predicted what was about to happen…

We just released an “After Movie” from FHL 2020, and it INSTANTLY gets me back in state to continue to create… to work… to serve!!! I can only hope it does the same for you :)

node.text: How she changed her life by launching an ebook telling her most vulnerable story...

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on July 29, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people and text that says 'YOU'RE PROBABLY 1 OR 2 KNOCKOUTS AWAY FROM SUCCESS... @RUSSELLBRUNSON GET BACK UP, PUT THE GLOVES BACK ON, AND GO BACK INTO THE RING ONE MORE TIME'.

node.text:
You never know how close to success you are, and you’ll never find out if you stop now!!! Just because you got knocked down doesn’t mean you won’t win…

You could be just 1 or 2 “knockouts” away from success, but the only way to find out is if you get up, get refocused, and get back out to the ring, to the mat, to the field, to the classroom, to the stage…to LIFE…and give it your all!! 

Give me a “💪” if nothing is going to keep you down!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on July 28, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of 2 people and text that says '手 TRAFFC Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 Keep putting your voice and your message out there... because when all is said and done, all that matters is the impact you have on people's lives.'.

node.text:
This journey and this mission aren’t about us… it’s about the people that are listening to you whose lives are being changed because of your message. Imagine if you stopped sharing it… what would happen to them?

They need you, they need your voice, they need your message!!! Your people are waiting to hear from you… so keep putting it out there… and it’ll be worth it in the end, I promise you that.

So whatever you do… don't stop putting your voice and message out there, because that’s how you’re going to make a true IMPACT on people’s lives!!! Who's with me?! :)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Brunson on July 27, 2021 tagging @cocalettie. May be an image of 2 people, airplane and indoor.

node.text: Happy birthday to my partner in crime, @cocalettie!! So grateful for the day you were born, but even more grateful for the life you live! You’re an amazing mom, wife and friend. I love you!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
This is something I think all of us fall into the habit of doing, and it only serves to limit us from reaching our full potential…

Don’t ever attach yourself to a person, a company, a place or a project… ONLY attach yourself to a mission, calling, or purpose…

And THAT’S how you will keep your power and your peace!

 Who’s with me?!?

node.text:
The biggest thing you should be focusing on right now is becoming obsessed with the people you’re trying to serve….

The more obsessed you are with them and who they are, what they like, what their journey is like, what they do, and so on.. the easier this game becomes because then you know exactly who your message is for, and what they need from you :)

So... are you OBSESSED?!?

So let’s hear it!!! What Funnels are you working on this weekend?! Drop your answer in the comments below 👇

node.text:
People will throw stones at you, but it’s up to you to decide what to do with them…

You could throw them back, and feed into the negativity, or you could use them to build something bigger... ;)

I’ll always choose to build something bigger with what’s thrown at me :) What about you?

May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 ㅇㅇ° There are 4 types of wealth: 1. Financial wealth (money) 2. Social wealth (status) 3. Time wealth (freedom) 4. Physical wealth (health)'.

node.text:
Your time and health are priceless…

We only have one life to live on this earth… so stop chasing things that won’t matter in the end!!!

The work we do to accomplish our mission in life is vital, but having the time and health to be able to fulfill that mission is what makes it all possible! So make sure you aren’t selling yourself short and being robbed of them!!!

I’m curious to know… what type of wealth do you wish to have more of right now? Leave your answer in the comments below!!!

node.text:
This one is for all my fellow introverts out there… :)

I want you to know how possible it is to succeed in what seems like an extrovert’s world!

It’s going to be hard and you’re going to suck at first, and that’s okay…we all do! But the more you put your message out there, the better you become…

Because at the end of the day, the only thing that truly matters is the impact you have on people’s lives, so stick to it… it’s worth it :)

#introvert #focusonyou #happiness #extrovert #obsessed #perspective #faith #opportunity #lifetime #successtips #businesstips #goalgetters #buildingmybrand #successfulmindset #entrepreneurmotivation #greatideas #agreeable #takeaction #nevergiveup #motivationalspeech #businesspassion #marketingcampaign #themomentisnow #love #stayfocused #bepositive #overdeliver #russellbrunson

May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'DEANGRAZIOS RAZIOSI BEAN TRAFFIC SECRETS IE RUSSELL S BRUNSON Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 208 231 3797 All of the missed parties, being criticized and misunderstood, the late nights and early mornings... it'll all pay off... Keep going!'.

node.text:
I promise you everything is going to be worth it…

The missed parties, being misunderstood and criticized, staying up late and waking up early… all of your hard work and effort, it’s all going to pay off! You just have to KEEP GOING!!!

You’re not doing all of this for nothing… you have a reason, a purpose, a mission, and it’s your job to keep pushing through no matter what. I promise it’s going to be worth it :)

Who’s with me on this?! Let me know!!!
